            "Researches competitors and gaps",
            "Produces complete PRD with tech stack recommendation",
            "PRD approved by user before handoff"
          ],
          "existing": "Prompt exists at prompts/consultant.md"
        },
        {
          "name": "Planner Agent Implementation",
          "description": "Full implementation of Planner Agent - PRD to atomic task plan",
          "acceptance_criteria": [
            "Accepts PRD JSON input",
            "Produces atomic tasks with prompt packets",
            "Each task 95%+ confidence score",
